# ❄️ Through the Snowstorm: a website-story

An interactive one-page website about a mysterious expedition, hand-made in HTML/CSS. Inspired by visual novels and the atmosphere of detectives.

## 🔧 Technologies
- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (Vanilla)
- Adaptive layout
- Hand-made styling without frameworks

